REMINDER: Final JSON keys: "summary" (string), "comments" (array of {file_path,line_number,severity,message}), "confidence_evaluations" (array), "investigation_complete" (bool), "loop_complete" (bool). No other top-level keys. No HTML in message strings. line_number is the "N | " annotation shown on the cited line (new-file line number) — never count lines yourself.
